        public void fromIfx(byte[] b,
           int offset,
           int length)
             throws java.sql.SQLException
        fromIfx() convert network complex type data into a IfxColumnInfo [] to hold the type information based on the flag information determine if it's NULL instantiate a IfxComplexInput to hold the serialized data. Data isn't materialized until Struct.getAttribute, Array.toArray() or IfxRow.toObject() or IfxCollection.toObject() is called.
